{"tid":1348302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【政府將上環及元朗事件混為一談 鄭松泰質疑為實施戒嚴鋪路】","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T03:11:21.000Z","uid":107060,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6f3cab7f55672e08593400b392e63f93754ac6","tid":1348302,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:12.000Z","msg":"昨晚衝擊中聯辦事件與元朗白衣人無差別政擊市民事件發生之後，不少建制中人都將兩件事混為一談。政府凌晨發聲明，一併譴責上環及元朗事件。 熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰去信保安局，批評特區政府把元朗的流氓暴行，與上環反對專制極權的示威混為一談，為實施戒嚴鋪路。 鄭松泰認為，香港陷入了人人自危的絕境，他強烈譴責林鄭月娥政府，要求林鄭月娥政府立即下台。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201907/64482468_10157328451721252_1155635318347530240_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201907%2F64482468_10157328451721252_1155635318347530240_n.jpg&h=ecefa76c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3dc6517ac70d93475966deae2d6c95e425220ae9","tid":1348302,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:55:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6d5a822d88f22e0d3d3cfeb648c6fc1ea3f399","tid":1348302,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7612781221721c059992bf75c224c7b9244f717","tid":1348302,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:04:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697380735826218c85c6ccc15f5038c0b6415eee","tid":1348302,"uid":199709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:05:32.000Z","msg":"上環Video 整合 (粗略) <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1348232/page/1</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346116/page/1</a> <br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=c7b57a6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=f29b92f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=206bac67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=6cf59ed0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=2443a814\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=475baaec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=07dc5f1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=61afac05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=381b7394\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=26664414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n <br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=fc788238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=bc975714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=c22220cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=56eb76e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=e783a202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n黑警用催淚彈直射向記者 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=d13770ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplePhotographers%2Fphotos%2Fa.1131233677080155%2F1131269430409913%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=86a6ff94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n（07.21）譴責警察暴力：記者被催淚彈打中，係直接打中！ <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=d13770ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n7.21民陣大遊行 | 警方平射角度開槍清場 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEsy4jTTOpYI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=7339a808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n有記者直接被催淚彈打中 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTeVHAuMLP4&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=8ee4b851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4</a><br />\n有義士腳部中槍 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157863977222448%3Fs%3D1279554103%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=9f75d5fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n【2225 上環】警方施放多枚催淚彈，其後多部警車在警察防線後方鳴笛 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182\" data-